title: f
first: Sen Pei, a research scientist in the Columbia University Mailman School of Public Health, and colleagues built a Covid-19 transmission model that looked at all US counties from February 21 through May 3.
second: Delaware's state-mandated Covid-19 mitigation efforts and investigations dramatically reduced the number of Covid-19 cases, hospitalizations and deaths earlier this year, according to a study published Friday in the US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention's Morbidity and Mortality Report.
